StorytellingData.Title:
Interference <size=80%><color=orange>://Ext</color></size>
- Finalize
StorytellingData.SurfaceDescription:
//:General Blueprint data is needed for new Rundown Protocol
 - <s>Locate a Central nFrame Cluster in this Sector.</s>
 - Repair Essential Maintanance System
 - Establish External Connection if possible

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
<color=red>[ERR://#005 Unexpected Network Condition During COMM]</color> is needed.
Administrator DNA verify is needed for further progress.
Prisoners sent to collect DNA sample from HSU unit.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..It's all done! We finally can be fre-
<size=200%><color=red>>[Alarm siren]</color></size>
>..Shit SHIT!
>[unintelligible, gunfire]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
DNA Data has been salvaged and ready to be uploaded.
Prisoners sent to Establish Uploading Protocol.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..I can't... breathe...
<color=red><size=200%>>..Yeah, do NOT go inside this fucking fog.</size></color>
>..Terminal system says there is fog turbine somewhere...

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Prisoners sent to try manual verification using salvaged Data Sphere.
Clear a Pathway If possible.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>[loud hum]
<size=200%><color=red>>..Why is this place so big?</color></size>
>..I know as little as you do.
>..Shit.. security alarm... again!

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Retrieved Data from [0<size=70%>X</size>E001] has processed.
Executing Finalize Protocol, Access to Eastern part of this complex is required.
Prisoners sent to startup reactor to gain access.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..Hey, this door seems to be opened?
<color=red><size=150%>>..Great... now they can come from BOTH FUCKING SIDE!</size></color>
>..Calm down
>..There's no other option now.. I'll take left side!

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Low-power level detected for powerline in this part of Complex, Immediate Restoration Required.
Prisoners sent to restore the air ventilization system in order to reach subjacent passage floor.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..Hey.. Is this fog... it's moving!?
<size=150%><color=red>>Yeah, We should hurry!</color></size>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Power outage occurred due to restart of air ventilization system for subjacent floor.
Prisoners sent to execute startup sequence for backup reactor.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..The verification time... it... What...?
>[Alarm Siren]
<color=red>>..Yeah we don't have enough time, We should split up!</color>
>..Are you ready?

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Navigational Beacon for [0<size=70%>X</size>D001] has been encrypted and can't be triggered.
Prisoners sent to collect PDECs (Partial Decoders) in complex.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>[Tracker humming]
>..There are...
>[pause]
>..What? What is it?
<color=red><size=200%>>....Don't.. Fucking... Mov-</size></color>
>[commotion, sudden scream]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Cargo from [0<size=70%>X</size>A001] contains useful parts for [Fog Repeller Beacon]
Unseal it and bring the content to extraction point.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>[metallic banging]
<color=red><size=150%>>..They sound angry, don't they?</size></color>
>..Yeah it does, And they are screaming from every fucking direction.
>..At least we have some tripmines.

>..Class.. Unknown?
>..This one is Unknown too.
<color=red><size=200%>>Well, Every fucking door is unknown!</size></color>
>..Is there a terminal?
[radio static]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Non-Authorized Access from Previous Expedition has Reported.
Prisoners sent to disable the Alarm in this floor.
<color=red>WARNING://Alarm Triggered!</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..Overload Bulkhead?
<color=red><size=200%>>..Yeah, this is our only chance to access it.</color></size>
>[distant scream]
>..Aw Fuck!
>[gunfire, screams]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
High Infection Barrier is blocking pathway to [0<size=70%>X</size>EEE2]
Allocating [Fog Repeller Beacon] to Expendable prisoners to clear a path.

General Power supply now in stable level.
Execute Final setup sequence at any cost of prisoners.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..This place is so fucking dark...
<color=red><size=200%>>..Where the fuck are the generators?!</size></color>
>..Shhhhh... They're pulsating!
>..Stand still...
>[radio static]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
nFrame Cluster has been located.
Prisoners sent to Clear a path towards [0<size=70%>X</size>E001]
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>[metallic banging]
>..The door..
<color=red><size=200%>>..It's opening itself!</size></color>
>Hold your ground!
>[unintelligible, gunfire]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Unexpected Fog Anomaly in this complex, Estimated Fatality Rate is in Extreme level.
Prisoners sent to restore partial climate control system in order to reach [0<size=70%>X</size>E001]

Retrieve Geo-data from nFrame using allocated Data Sphere.
Prisoners deemed expendable.
<color=red>#E_RR: Security Alarm Override Failure on $Z_???</color>
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..Found that nFrame here!
<color=red><size=200%>>..Put it in, Right NOW!</size></color>
>[machinery sound, distant roar]
>[lost communication]

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription:
Closing Rundown Session::SubComplex: [91X122]
Extract Essential Items from this part of facility

Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>..Wait it's all Hub_HA_01..?
>..Always had been
>[gunfire, lost communication]
